<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٣٢١٢ -<span style="color:#006d98"> وَبِهِ عَنِ الْحَسَنِ قَالَ:</span> <span style="color:#6c6c00">«كُلُّ صَلَاةٍ بَعْدَ الْعِشَاءِ الْآخِرَةِ فَهِيَ نَاشِئَةُ اللَّيْلِ»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>